graph TD
    accTitle: SaaS Growth Framework
    accDescr: A comprehensive flowchart detailing the stages of growing a Software as a Service business from foundation to scaling.

    subgraph Phase1 [Stage 1: Foundation & Product-Market Fit]
        A[Identify Pain Point] --> B[MVP Development]
        B --> C[Beta Testing & Feedback]
        C --> D{Product-Market Fit?}
        D -- No --> B
        D -- Yes --> E[Define Ideal Customer Profile - ICP]
    end

    subgraph Phase2 [Stage 2: Acquisition & Lead Gen]
        E --> F[Content Marketing/SEO]
        E --> G[Paid Ads - Search/Social]
        E --> H[Cold Outbound/Social Selling]
        F & G & H --> I[Landing Page & Free Trial/Freemium]
    end

    subgraph Phase3 [Stage 3: Activation & Retention]
        I --> J[Onboarding Workflow]
        J --> K[Aha! Moment]
        K --> L[Subscription Conversion]
        L --> M[Customer Success Management]
        M --> N{Churn Analysis}
        N -- High Churn --> J
        N -- Low Churn --> O[Expansion/Upsell]
    end

    subgraph Phase4 [Stage 4: Scaling & Optimization]
        O --> P[Referral Programs]
        O --> Q[Partnerships & Integrations]
        O --> R[PLG - Product Led Growth]
        P & Q & R --> S[Revenue Compounding]
    end

